            "title": "將軍澳日出康城男疑縱火燒郵筒  消防救熄信件幸保不失",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/87c97f6828691cdaee6438d0eef267fd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250207/_2025020700354855865.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">尹敬堂攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>將軍澳發生懷疑縱火案。昨日（6日）晚上10時許，一名女途人在日出康城巴士總站扶手電梯旁，發現一名男子疑似在點燃物件並焚燒一個郵筒的外部，於是報警。\n\n</p>\n<p>消防趕抵現場，迅速將火救熄，並打開郵筒查看，初步確定郵筒內的信件並無損毀。警員和消防到場前，涉案男子已遁去無踪，暫未有人被捕。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4064339/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05141946dee2e7a5ffedd718fbbeb73b/2025-02/13_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4064340/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86b9f1dfdca350d34a72c75256937c77/2025-02/12_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4064341/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/983671525469912cebd5368e6f7cb946/2025-02/15_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4064342/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff0855f5cef2d617baa73fd44d1516e6/2025-02/14_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4064343/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd2ec9d9744bffb19061c23548290db2/2025-02/11_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=