        {
            "title": "衛詩雅婚禮將近好緊張與未婚夫互相安慰：瞓覺都扎醒     荷蘭行超市被外籍觀眾認到獲讚《破•地獄》好睇",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"衛詩雅婚禮將近好緊張與未婚夫互相安慰：瞓覺都扎醒     荷蘭行超市被外籍觀眾認到獲讚《破•地獄》好睇\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fd034e50f20283fc3fc12f2ceead1edb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020623285837079.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">衛詩雅婚禮將近好緊張與未婚夫互相安慰：瞓覺都扎醒     荷蘭行超市被外籍觀眾認到獲讚《破•地獄》好睇</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>衛詩雅今晚（6日）出席《香港專業電影攝影師學會37週年晚宴》，衛詩雅表示剛從荷蘭鹿特丹返港，因代表《破•地獄》參與影展，並逗留一星期，是她婚前最後一個旅程，獨自搭飛機到當地感覺特別。\n\n</p><h2>衛詩雅與未婚夫互相安慰</h2>\n<p>衛詩雅又大爆當地觀眾很喜歡該片，有一日自己行超市，獲外籍觀眾大讚該片好睇，估不到在好遠地方上映也獲認同，她覺得是婚前最好的禮物。提到婚禮將近，她笑言最近先識緊張，瞓覺都會扎醒，亦發現好多事未做，但未婚夫比她更緊張，所以互相安慰，亦提醒對方婚禮當日只經歷10小時好似陣痛就會過去。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅奪得「攝影師眼中最具魅力女演員獎」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7512e257d9db30a5df1304d9f087ce9/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-06_at_10_09_08_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅奪得「攝影師眼中最具魅力女演員獎」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅表示開心能與林峯同樣獲獎。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1312c3117b0a6ad2f5e1d2db5f559e92/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_210433639_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅表示開心能與林峯同樣獲獎。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅剛從荷蘭鹿特丹返港，因代表《破•地獄》參與影展。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8467ef44420bd2e2c8d33f2ad29d46b9/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_210433639_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅剛從荷蘭鹿特丹返港，因代表《破•地獄》參與影展。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅透露有日在荷蘭行超市，獲外籍觀眾大讚《破•地獄》好睇。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a2c6b3321ad7a46c66c2ddb4e63295a/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_210433639_16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅透露有日在荷蘭行超市，獲外籍觀眾大讚《破•地獄》好睇。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"提到婚禮將近，她表示近先識緊張，仲會連瞓覺都扎醒！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a075fcd6b2d14c6facd4bff833e08d2/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250206_210433639_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        提到婚禮將近，她表示近先識緊張，仲會連瞓覺都扎醒！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅近日在社交網貼上與未婚夫的結婚照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f17710bc15505de1c6ce1c7061ab2c90/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-06_at_11_16_02_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅近日在社交網貼上與未婚夫的結婚照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>衛詩雅跟林峯同樣獲獎感開心</h2>\n<p>談到她奪得「攝影師眼中最具魅力女演員獎」，她表示很開心，尤其得到攝影師投票得獎大感觸，因為入行16、7年，當中拍戲未必做主角，但攝影師不時會提點她。談到可覺自己有魅力？她坦言不知道要別人講，但跟林峯同樣獲獎很開心，又認為對方是自備魅力。問到覺得林峯定未婚夫有魅力？她即謂未婚夫。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
